# Versioning

- **Single source:** `src/utils/app-version.ts` — update `appVersion` on every code change.
- **Format:** `Major.Basic.FrontendMinor.BackendMinor` (e.g. `1.2.9.9`)
- **Bump:** FE-only → 3rd segment; BE-only → 4th; both → both; major/basic → 1st/2nd as appropriate.
- **File headers:** `@latest app version: x.y.z` in edited files (not `@version`).
